  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study focuses on the difficulties to maintain a weight loss and behavioural change after
      having been in a institutional intermittent weight loss programme.

      We explore if including a member of the family or a close friend in the treatment influences
      weight loss maintenance after completion of the programme.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
